
Edited conclusion: Compare to any other majors, HCDE is innovative major in upcoming years. As mentioned above, it takes the user into account and designing systems and interfaces that accommodate their needs. In these days, especially in great Seattle area, as the requirements of UX/UI designers are progressively increasing since human interfaces consider most important issues in these days, there are many jobs offered from the companies such as Facebook, Amazon, Microsoft, and many start-ups that require UX/UI designers. 
